review_blob: Great for lovers of a good, bitter IPA. Pours hazy gold with a thin head. Beautiful fruity flowery aroma, nice bitter taste on the front and a solid aftertaste. Not too complex but a solid IPA with a tasty rye flavor
beer_name: Harpoon 100 Barrel Series #37 - Rich & Dans Rye IPA

review_blob: Got at the harpoon beer hall on tap. Pours a black coffee color with a huge foamy tan head... Maybe 2 inches? Had a rich pumpkin flavor and a heavy aftertaste on the palate. Something I would definitely have again
Average, nothing too special. Pours with a small head, pale gold color. Has a soft apple flavor with a hint of pumpkin.
